---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();

const footerLinks = {
  services: [
    { href: '/simulateur', label: 'Simulateur d\'économies' },
    { href: '/comparatifs/pac-vs-chaudiere-bois', label: 'Comparatif PAC vs Chaudière' },
    { href: '/experts', label: 'Trouver un expert RGE' }
  ],
  ressources: [
    { href: '/blog', label: 'Conseils énergie' },
    { href: '/blog/explosion-tarifs-electricite-2026', label: 'Hausse des tarifs 2026' },
    { href: '/blog/panneaux-solaires-rentabilite', label: 'Rentabilité solaire' }
  ],
  legal: [
    { href: '/mentions-legales', label: 'Mentions légales' },
    { href: '/politique-confidentialite', label: 'Politique de confidentialité' }
  ]
};
---

<footer class="bg-navy-900 text-white">
  <div class="border-b border-navy-700">
    <div class="container-custom mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-navy-200">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="font-medium">Données sécurisées RGPD</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-navy-200">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="font-medium">Experts certifiés RGE</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-navy-200">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.121 15.536c-1.171 1.952-3.07 1.952-4.242 0-1.172-1.953-1.172-5.119 0-7.072 1.171-1.952 3.07-1.952 4.242 0M8 10.5h4m-4 3h4m9-1.5a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="font-medium">Service 100% gratuit</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container-custom mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-10">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-emerald-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="font-display font-bold text-xl">
            Rénov<span class="text-emerald-400">Action</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-navy-300 mb-6 max-w-sm">
          Calculez vos économies d'énergie et trouvez les meilleures solutions de rénovation énergétique avec nos experts certifiés RGE.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Services</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {footerLinks.services.map(link => (
            <li>
              <a href={link.href} class="text-navy-300 hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">
                {link.label}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Ressources</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {footerLinks.ressources.map(link => (
            <li>
              <a href={link.href} class="text-navy-300 hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">
                {link.label}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Informations</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {footerLinks.legal.map(link => (
            <li>
              <a href={link.href} class="text-navy-300 hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">
                {link.label}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="border-t border-navy-700">
    <div class="container-custom mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-navy-400">
        <p>© {currentYear} RénovAction. Tous droits réservés. Service indépendant non affilié à l'État.</p>
        <p>Sources : <a href="https://www.ademe.fr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-emerald-400">ADEME</a> • <a href="https://www.ecologie.gouv.fr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-emerald-400">Min. Transition Écologique</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
